          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">📥 Get Started Today</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-700">AdShield Pro makes browsing cleaner, faster, and more private — without complicated settings or invasive tracking. Whether you start with the free version or go for Pro for advanced control, you're taking a big step toward a better web experience.</p>
